">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<ol class=\"breadcrumb\"><li class=\"breadcrumb-item\"><a href=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/\">ホーム</a></li><li class=\"breadcrumb-item is-current\">採用情報</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</nav>\t\t<div class=\"page-contents\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"recruit-main\"><!-- \n\n<p class=\"recruit-main__text\">\n    <img class=\"pc-block\" src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-main_text.svg\" alt=\"\">\n    <img class=\"sp-block\" src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-main_text_sp.svg\" alt=\"\">\n  </p>\n\n --><!-- \n\n<p class=\"recruit-main__visual\">\n    <img class=\"pc-block\" src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-main_visual-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n    <img class=\"sp-block\" src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-main_visual-scaled_sp.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n  </p>\n\n --></p>\n<p class=\"recruit-main__catch\"><img src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-main_catch.svg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p class=\"recruit-main__copy\"><img class=\"pc-block\" src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-main_copy.svg\" alt=\"\" /> <img class=\"sp-block\" src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-main_copy_sp.svg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p class=\"recruit-main__link\"><a href=\"/recruit/ceo-message/\">社長メッセージへ</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"recruit-works\">\n<p class=\"recruit-works__content\"><img class=\"pc-block\" src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-works.png\" alt=\"\" /> <img class=\"sp-block\" src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-works_sp.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"recruit-requirements\">\n<p class=\"recruit-requirements__title\"><img class=\"pc-block\" src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-requirements_title.svg\" alt=\"\" /> <img class=\"sp-block\" src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-requirements_title_sp.svg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<div class=\"recruit-requirements__content\">\n<div class=\"recruit-requirements__img\"><img src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-requirements_01.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<div class=\"recruit-requirements__text\">\n<p><img src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-requirements_4k.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>建設業は、1980年代頃から3Kの職業と言われ、<br />「きつい」「汚い」「危険」な仕事とされてきました。<br />当社では<span class=\"red\">「給料の適正化」「完全週休二日制の導入」</span><br /><span class=\"red\">「やりがいを感じられる仕事」「デジタル化の推進」</span>を目指しております。<br />変わりゆく建設業界で、私たちと一緒に自信と誇りの持てる仕事をしてみませんか？</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"recruit-requirements__links\">\n<p><a href=\"/recruit/freshers/\">新卒採用はこちら</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/recruit/careerrecruit\">キャリア採用はこちら</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"recruit-requirements__mail\">\n<p class=\"text\"><span class=\"d-inline-block\">採用につきましては、</span><span class=\"d-inline-block\">お気軽にお問い合わせください。</span></p>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-12 col-md-6\">\n<p class=\"num\"><span class=\"small\">TEL</span>018-823-8146</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-12 col-md-6\">\n<p class=\"num\"><span class=\"small\">FAX</span>018-824-2164</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"manager\">(管理部　伊藤まで)</p>\n<div class=\"btn-maill\"><a href=\"/contact/\">メールでのお問い合わせはこちら</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"recruit-about\">\n<p class=\"recruit-about__title\"><img class=\"pc-block\" src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-about_title.svg\" alt=\"\" /> <img class=\"sp-block\" src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-about_title_sp.svg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<div class=\"recruit-about__content\">\n<div class=\"recruit-about__icon\"><a class=\"d-inline-block\" href=\"/recruit/about/#about-01\"> <img src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-about_01.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n<div class=\"recruit-about__icon\"><a class=\"d-inline-block\" href=\"/recruit/about/#about-02\"> <img src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-about_02.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n<div class=\"recruit-about__icon\"><a class=\"d-inline-block\" href=\"/recruit/about/#about-03\"> <img src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-about_03.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"recruit-banner\">\n<div class=\"recruit-banner__title\"><img class=\"pc-block\" src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-banner_title.png\" alt=\"\" /> <img class=\"sp-block\" src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-banner_title_sp.svg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<div class=\"recruit-banner__content\">\n<p><a href=\"/recruit/message\"> <img src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-banner_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> </a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/recruit/careerup\"> <img src=\"http://www.yamani-s.co.jp/yamani-cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/img_recruit-banner_02.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> </a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</article>\n</main>\n    <footer class=\"footer\" role=\"contentinfo\">\n        <nav class=\"footer-nav--wrap\" role=\"navigation\" aria-label=\"このサイトについて\">\n            <ul class=\"footer-nav container\">\n                <!-- <li class=\"footer-nav--item\"><a href=\